data.description: Welcome Home to your 3.47 acre Getaway! You won't find a Better Neighborhood or Location then this! This two Story Home has a Spacious entry level with a Designated Dining area, Large Great Room with high Ceilings, and gourmet kitchen with breakfast area. Primary Bedroom on Entry level with walk in Closet, and a Recently Remodeled Private Bathroom. Upstairs you have 3 additional Bedrooms, with another Full Bath! Enjoy the back  porch, as you enjoy cookouts with friends, or a night of Star gazing. This Home is a Must See, so don't miss your opportunity to tour today!
